The evidence with the title 'The G.O.P. is fooling itself on taxes - The New York Times ' says Nov 18, 2017  ... Once Republican leaders filled their plan with tax cuts for the wealthy , they didn't have much money left for the middle class . In the Senate, Republicans were so desperate to find money that this past week they released a new version of the bill that made virtually all of the middle - class tax cuts temporary. 
